OL,3,CWoman found guilty of four historical
OL,4,Coffences against a child
OL,6,FA 56-year-old woman has been found
OL,7,Fguilty of four offences against a
OL,8,Fchild in Jersey.
OL,10,FBeverley Rose Colley's crimes
OL,11,Fconsisted of common assaults and
OL,12,Fintentionally causing harm to a child,
OL,13,Fwhich took place between 2000 and 2019.
OL,15,FShe was found guilty at Jersey's Royal
OL,16,FCourt on 13 March 2026, following a
OL,17,Ffour-day trial.
OL,19,FThe court will reconvene in a week's
OL,20,Ftime on 20 March, to decide a date for
OL,21,FColley's sentencing.
