OL,3,CWoman found guilty of four historical
OL,4,Coffences against a child
OL,6,FA report of the historical allegations
OL,7,Fwas first made to Jersey Police in
OL,8,FApril 2024, which was followed by an
OL,9,Finvestigation.
OL,11,FColley was charged for her crimes in
OL,12,FJune 2025.
OL,14,FFollowing the verdict, States of
OL,15,FJersey Police added: "These historical
OL,16,Foffences caused serious and lasting
OL,17,Fharm to the victim, and the impact
OL,18,Fcontinues to be felt today. Today's
OL,19,Fverdict reinforces that violence and
OL,20,Fabuse in any form are never acceptable
OL,21,Fand will not be tolerated."
