OL,3,CWoman found guilty of four historical
OL,4,Coffences against a child
OL,6,F"Any reports made to the States of
OL,7,FJersey Police will be fully
OL,8,Finvestigated with support and guidance
OL,9,Foffered and provided by our partner
OL,10,Fagencies.
OL,12,F"We commend the victim's courage in
OL,13,Fcoming forward, supporting a police
OL,14,Finvestigation, and ultimately seeing
OL,15,Fthe case through to a Royal Court
OL,16,Ftrial."
